<p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247141342034954.jpg" title="1731247141342034954.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215016.jpg" width="749" height="441" style="width: 749px; height: 441px;"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2024年11月9日是第33个&quot;全国消防日&quot;， 今年的主题是全民消防、生命至上学一点消防知识，添一份平安幸福现在一起来了解关于消防安全的相关知识吧！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247160375038167.jpg" title="1731247160375038167.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215008.jpg" width="815" height="851" style="width: 815px; height: 851px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp;生产生活中常见的火灾类型有哪些该如何防范这份防火安全知识手册一起学起来吧！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247219178090038.jpg" title="1731247219178090038.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215022.jpg" width="822" height="2012" style="width: 822px; height: 2012px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247262695030582.jpg" title="1731247262695030582.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215059.jpg" width="823" height="2200" style="width: 823px; height: 2200px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247311977034143.jpg" title="1731247311977034143.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215045.jpg" width="824" height="2565" style="width: 824px; height: 2565px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247348539046468.jpg" title="1731247348539046468.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215053.jpg" width="821" height="2175" style="width: 821px; height: 2175px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247395456061853.jpg" title="1731247395456061853.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215106.jpg" width="824" height="2570" style="width: 824px; height: 2570px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241110/1731247436485054114.jpg" title="1731247436485054114.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241110215141.jpg" width="823" height="2653" style="width: 823px; height: 2653px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">冬季是火灾多发的季节</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">11月份进入冬季，天气干燥</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">是火灾的高发期</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">火灾发生在校园</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">将会导致严重的财产损失以及大量的人员伤亡</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在此也特别提醒大家做好火灾防控工作</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">拉开冬防序幕</span></p><p><br/></p>